@startuml
title Diagram Workflow Overview

actor "Developer" as Dev
participant "diagram-workflow" as Skill
participant "PlantUML source" as Puml
participant "ASCII render" as Md

Dev -> Skill : request diagram
Skill -> Puml : write source
Skill -> Skill : choose diagram type
Skill -> Md : render text diagram
Skill --> Dev : review and refine

@enduml
